## 🔎 Finding XSS — Checklist

- [ ] Test all input fields (search, login, register, comments)
- [ ] Test URL parameters
- [ ] Test HTTP headers (User-Agent, Referer, X-Forwarded-For)
- [ ] Test file upload filenames
- [ ] Test JSON input fields
- [ ] Check error messages (reflect input?)
- [ ] Test hidden form fields
- [ ] Check 404 pages

