## 🧠 eWPTXv3 Tips

- Always check for **DOM XSS** in single-page applications (React, Angular, Vue)
- Look for **postMessage** misuse
- Check **innerHTML, document.write, eval()** usage in JS
- Test **SVG files** for XSS
- Try XSS in **PDF generation** endpoints
- Check for **mXSS** (mutation XSS) in rich text editors

